RESTful ROUTES:
VERB                ROUTES                  DESC
GET             /api/todos              List all todos
POST            /api/todos              Create new todo
GET             /api/todos/:todoId      Retrieve a todo
PUT             /api/todos/:totoId      Update a todo
DELETE          /api/todos/:todoId      Delete a todo
 
1. An api using mongoose for MongoDB and express on NodeJS.
2. A simple todolist app on top of the todo api.